---
title: Saucy Tomato & Spinach Gnocchi with Garlic Pangrattato & Plant-Based Basil Pesto
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in a rich and creamy plant-based tomato sauce, then baked until deliciously
golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.
